### Requirements

#### 1. Full-Screen Hero with Scroll-Flip Effect
Hero must be `100vh - 80px` with scroll-flip transition matching Landing Page.

**Key patterns in LandingPage.tsx:**
- `heroRef` + scroll listener â†’ `scrollProgress` state
- Hero transform: `perspective(1000px) rotateX(${scrollProgress * -8}deg)`
- Content wrapper with opacity/translate tied to scroll
- Scroll indicator button at bottom

#### 2. Color Strategy (IMPORTANT - NOT Same Colors Everywhere)

**Brand Foundation (consistent across all pages):**
- Dark backgrounds: `charcoal-900` / `#0B1A14`
- Primary green: `forest-500/600/700`
- Accent gold: `gold-400/500/600`
- Light backgrounds: `ivory`, `cream`, `white`

**Page-Specific Accent Colors (create variety):**
Each page should have a PRIMARY ACCENT based on its purpose:

| Page | Primary Accent | Reason |
|------|----------------|--------|
| Landing | Gold | Premium, aspirational |
| Academy | Gold + Amber warmth | Education, achievement |
| Solutions/Staffing | Forest green | Trust, growth, stability |
| Cross-Border | Purple tints | Global, innovation |
| Industries | Slate/Blue | Professional, corporate |
| Careers | Emerald | Opportunity, fresh start |
| Contact | Warm gold | Approachable, inviting |
| About | Forest + Gold balanced | Brand story |

**How to apply:**
- Hero gradient tints
- Section accent bars on cards
- CTA button colors
- Icon background colors
- Badge/tag colors

The brand palette is consistent; the EMPHASIS shifts per page.

---

#### 3. Design Patterns

**Section Headers:**
<div className="flex items-center gap-3 mb-6">
<div className="w-12 h-px bg-gold-500" />
<span className="text-gold-600 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.2em]">
Section Label
</span>
</div>


**Card Accents:** Left-side colored bars (1px width, full height)

**CTAs:** Angled clip-path, NOT rounded-full

**Backgrounds:** Organic radial gradients with irregular shapes

